title: Naturally Good To Go
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Kitchen and juice bar inside the health food store. Offers grab n go food packaged in to-go ware. Vegans ask to omit cheese, etc. Closes 30 minutes before the store does.
